last_episode_to_air.name: 205 Live #270
last_episode_to_air.overview: Ikemen Jiro faces Trick Williams. Lash Legend takes on Erica Yan. Joe Gacy battles Xyon Quinn.

name: WWE 205 Live
overview: WWE's division of Cruiserweight's battle it out to decide who is the greatest wrestler under 205lbs.

episodes.name: November 29, 2016 (Columbia, SC)
episodes.overview: This week on the debut episode of 205 Live, we will get an in-depth look at some of WWE’s greatest Cruiserweights. Plus, The Brian Kendrick defends his WWE Cruiserweight Championship against the outlandish Rich Swann. Also, we will have the debut of The Extraordinary Gentleman Jack Gallagher when he faces off with Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: December 6, 2016 (Houston, TX)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live we have a rematch from last week when the new Cruiserweight Champion Rich Swann defends his new title against the former champion The Brian Kendrick. Plus, the debut of Cedric Alexander as he faces off against the Scottish Supernova, Noam Dar. Also, we will take an in-depth look at Mustafa Ali.

episodes.name: December 13, 2016 (Philadelphia, PA)
episodes.overview: TJ Perkins takes on Rich Swann. Plus, the 205 Live debut of Mustafa Ali as he faces off with The Golden Lynx of Lucha Libre, Lince Dorado. Also, Gentleman Jack Gallagher goes one-on-one with Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: December 20, 2016 (Detroit, MI)
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Rich Swann teams up with TJ Perkins to take on Neville & The Brian Kendrick. Plus, The Golden Lynx of Lucha Libre Lince Dorado faces off with Ariya Daivari. Also, we will check in with the love triangle between Cedric Alexander, Alicia Fox, and Noam Dar.

episodes.name: December 27, 2016 (Chicago, IL)
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Rich Swann takes on his former mentor Neville in a colossal main event. Plus, after being called a scoundrel by Ariya Daivari, Jack Gallagher must restore his honor as he challenges Daivari to 205 Live's first-ever Duel. Also, Mustafa Ali is in action in his hometown of Chicago, Illinois.

episodes.name: January 3, 2017 (Jacksonville, FL)
episodes.overview: Neville tries to build on his momentum as he faces off with former WWE Cruiserweight Champion TJ Perkins in a massive main event. Plus, after defeating Ariya Daivari in a Gentlemen’s Duel, Jack Gallagher takes on The Premiere Athlete Tony Nese. Also, Tajiri makes his 205 Live debut.

episodes.name: January 10, 2017 (Baton Rouge, LA)
episodes.overview: The love triangle between Cedric Alexander, Alicia Fox, and Noam Dar hits a head as Alexander faces off with Dar. Plus, we have the parlay contract signing between Ariya Daivari and Jack Gallagher. Also, the WWE Cruiserweight Champion Rich Swann is in action as he takes on The Premiere Athlete Tony Nese.

episodes.name: January 17, 2017 (Memphis, TN)
episodes.overview: The epic rivalry between Ariya Daivari and Gentleman Jack Gallagher concludes as they go toe-to-toe in an "I Forfeit" Match. Mustafa Ali goes one-on-one with The Premier Athlete Tony Nese. Also, a preview of the Cruiserweight Championship match that will take place at the Royal Rumble when former friends Rich Swann and Neville face off.

episodes.name: January 24, 2017 (Toledo, OH)
episodes.overview: A mega main event as the self-proclaimed King of the Cruiserweights Neville faces off with Cedric Alexander just days before his WWE Cruiserweight Championship match at the Royal Rumble against the Champion Rich Swann. Also, The Premier Athlete Tony Nese goes one-on-one with TJ Perkins. Plus, The Brian Kendrick is in action.

episodes.name: January 31, 2017 (Corpus Christi, TX)
episodes.overview: A new No. 1 contender to Neville’s Cruiserweight Championship will be crowned this week on 205 Live.

episodes.name: February 7, 2017 (Seattle, WA)
episodes.overview: Five superstars face off to see who will become the new number one contender to Neville’s WWE Cruiserweight Championship in a colossal main event. Plus, The Golden Lynx of Lucha Libre, Lince Dorado takes on the brash and cocky, The Brian Kendrick. Also, we will preview a new Superstar who will be making his 205 Live debut next week.

episodes.name: February 14, 2017 (Anaheim, CA)
episodes.overview: The Cruiserweight Classic Winner TJ Perkins faces off with the WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville in an epic main event. Plus, you won’t be able to handle it when Rich Swann takes on the Scottish Supernova Noam Dar. Also, the High Flying Luchador known as Gran Metalik makes his 205 Live debut when he squares off with the Punishing Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: February 21, 2017 (Ontario, CA)
episodes.overview: The Premier Athlete Tony Nese goes one-on-one with the WWE Cruiserweight Championship Number One Contender, Gentleman Jack Gallagher in a huge main event. Plus, The Scottish Super Nova Noam Dar is in action as he faces off with Rich Swann. Also, Akira Tozawa seeks revenge from Monday Night RAW as he goes toe-to-toe with The Brian Kendrick.

episodes.name: February 28, 2017 (Saint Paul, MN)
episodes.overview: Sitting atop the Cruiserweight division as both champion and king, Neville issues a self-adulating and aggressive State of 205 Live address less than a week before his battle with Gentleman Jack Gallagher at WWE Fastlane.

episodes.name: March 7, 2017 (Indianapolis, IN)
episodes.overview: Austin Aries makes his 205 Live in-ring debut against the Premier Athlete Tony Nese in an epic main event. Also, Rich Swann and Gentleman Jack Gallagher team up to face the duo of Ariya Daivari and The Scottish Supernova Noam Dar in tag team action. Plus, Akira Tozawa seeks revenge as he faces off with the 'The Brian Kendrick'.

episodes.name: March 14, 2017 (Pittsburgh, PA)
episodes.overview: The entire course of the Cruiserweight Division is set to change in the main event, in a Fatal 5-Way Elimination Match to determine who will challenge Neville for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship at WrestleMania. Rich Swann and Gentleman Jack Gallagher unite to take on Ariya Daivari & Noam Dar, Mustafa Ali faces Drew Gulak, and more.

episodes.name: March 21, 2017 (Uncasville, CT)
episodes.overview: The WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville is in action as he faces off with Mustafa Ali. Also, TJ Perkins tries to settle a feud as he goes one-on-one with the Premier Athlete Tony Nese. Plus, Austin Aries, the Number One Contender for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship at WrestleMania, addresses his opponent Neville and the entire WWE Universe.

episodes.name: March 28, 2017 (Richmond, VA)
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville addresses the WWE Universe. Also, Akira Tozawa finally gets his opportunity to teach The Brian Kendrick a lesson. The always-entertaining Rich Swann is in action as he faces off with Ariya Daivari. Mustafa Ali is also in action as he shows off some off his high-flying skills.

episodes.name: April 4, 2017 (Orlando, FL)
episodes.overview: A Fatal 4-Way to determine who will become the new No. 1 Contender for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship. Akira Tozawa looks for retribution on The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Rich Swann reveals a secret that could change the entire landscape of 205 Live.

episodes.name: April 11, 2017 (Boston, MA)
episodes.overview: TJ Perkins plans to inflict punishment on Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Rich Swann looks to prove that he, not Noam Dar, has been the one sending the gifts to Alicia Fox. The Brian Kendrick takes on Mustafa Ali.

episodes.name: April 18, 2017 (Louisville, KY)
episodes.overview: TJ Perkins takes on the No. 1 Contender for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship, Austin Aries, in the main event. Ariya Daivari arrives in style as he takes on Mustafa Ali. Plus, Noam Dar looks to confront Rich Swann for making him look like a fool last week in front of Alicia Fox.

episodes.name: April 25, 2017 (Des Moines, IA)
episodes.overview: The WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville faces off with Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Akira Tozawa & Rich Swann join forces as they take on the team of Noam Dar & The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Mustafa Ali continues his brand of reckless in-ring action when he goes toe-to-toe with The Premier Athlete Tony Nese.

episodes.name: May 2, 2017 (Fresno, CA)
episodes.overview: Noam Dar looks for retribution against Rich Swann for causing Alicia Fox to break up with him. TJP faces off with Lince Dorado. Drew Gulak introduces Mustafa Ali to his vision of 205 Live and what the future holds for the entire Cruiserweight Division. Plus, Corey Graves sits down with The Brian Kendrick.

episodes.name: May 9, 2017 (London, ENG)
episodes.overview: 205 Live is in London, England. In our main event, Akira Tozawa faces The Brian Kendrick. Tony Nese looks to pick up a victory as he battles Mustafa Ali. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher has a special thank you planned for Austin Aries for saving him the night before on Raw.

episodes.name: May 16, 2017 (Manchester, NH)
episodes.overview: TJP gets one final chance to put Austin Aries out of commission for good and earn a Cruiserweight Championship match in the future. Plus, Mustafa Ali goes one-on-one with Tony Nese. Noam Dar looks to impress Alicia Fox as he takes on Gran Metalik. Plus, The Brian Kendrick has a message for his opponent next week, Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: May 23, 2017 (Toledo, OH)
episodes.overview: The Brian Kendrick and Akira Tozawa compete in a Street Fight. WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville and his challenger at Extreme Rules Austin Aries have a sit-down interview with Corey Graves. Plus, Cedric Alexander returns to 205 Live after being out of commission for three months with a knee injury.

episodes.name: May 30, 2017 (Atlanta, GA)
episodes.overview: Austin Aries addresses the WWE Universe before his WWE Cruiserweight Championship match against Neville at Extreme Rules. Mustafa Ali looks for revenge against Drew Gulak after he attacked him two weeks ago. Plus, Rich Swann takes on Noam Dar just days before their mixed tag match with Sasha Banks and Alicia Fox at Extreme Rules.

episodes.name: June 6, 2017 (Rochester, NY)
episodes.overview: The first WWE Cruiserweight Champion TJP takes on the current WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville in a match for the title. Cedric Alexander renews his rivalry with the Scottish Supernova Noam Dar when the two face off in singles action. Plus, Mustafa Ali continues to defend the high-flying 205 Live.

episodes.name: June 13, 2017 (New Orleans, LA)
episodes.overview: Akira Tozawa looks to help his case to become the No 1. Contender for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship when he takes on TJP. Austin Aries addresses the WWE Universe on his future. Plus, Cedric Alexander faces off with Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: June 20, 2017 (Dayton, OH)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann takes on Neville, hoping to earn a future Cruiserweight Championship Match. Gentleman Jack Gallagher looks for retribution from last week when he faces off with the Premier Athlete Tony Nese. Plus, Mustafa Ali and Drew Gulak face off in their third match in two months.

episodes.name: June 27, 2017 (San Diego, CA)
episodes.overview: The Cruiserweight Champion Neville shares his thoughts on facing Akira Tozawa at Great Balls Of Fire and Titus World Wide. Drew Gulak seeks retribution for his loss last week against Mustafa Ali. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher attempts to teach The Brian Kendrick some class when these two go head to head.

episodes.name: July 4, 2017 (Phoenix, AZ)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann and TJP face off in the main event. Titus O'Neil has words for Cruiserweight Champion Neville just days before O'Neil's client Akira Tozawa faces Neville for the Championship at Great Balls of Fire. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher looks for some retribution against the man who attacked him two weeks ago, The Premier Athlete Tony Nese.

episodes.name: July 11, 2017 (San Antonio, TX)
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander and Noam Dar face off in an "I Quit" Match. Rich Swann and TJP continue their friendly rivalry as TJP has a game for the two of them to play. Plus, Akira Tozawa shows why he deserves another Championship Championship Match when he takes on Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: July 18, 2017 (Birmingham, AL)
episodes.overview: Mustafa Ali and Drew Gulak determine whose style is the right one for 205 Live in a 2 out of 3 Falls match. The Brian Kendrick takes on Devin Bennett. Plus, Akira Tozawa tries to prove he doesn't need Titus Worldwide's help as he takes on Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: July 25, 2017 (Richmond, VA)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann & Cedric Alexander team up to face Tony Nese & TJP. The Brian Kendrick addresses the WWE Universe. Plus, Ariya Daivari tries to prove he deserves a WWE Cruiserweight Championship Match when he takes on current champion Neville.

episodes.name: August 1, 2017 (Cleveland, OH)
episodes.overview: Ariya Daivari and Akira Tozawa face off and the winner earns a WWE Cruiserweight Championship Match at SummerSlam. Gentleman Jack Gallagher gets his hands on The Brian Kendrick. Plus, The Premier Athlete Tony Nese takes on the high-flying Gran Metalik.

episodes.name: August 8, 2017 (Toronto, Ontario, CA)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann and TJP put their friendship to the test when they face off in the main event. Corey Graves sits down with the No. 1 Contender for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship, Akira Tozawa. Plus, The Scottish Supernova Noam Dar makes his return to 205 Live.

episodes.name: August 15, 2017 (Providence, RI)
episodes.overview: Titus Worldwide throws a celebration for new WWE Cruiserweight Champion Akira Tozawa. The Brian Kendrick faces off against Mustafa Ali. Plus, in tag team action, Drew Gulak & Tony Nese team up to face Cedric Alexander & Gran Metalik.

episodes.name: August 22, 2017 (Brooklyn, NY)
episodes.overview: In a SummerSlam rematch main event, Neville defends his newly-reclaimed Cruiserweight Championship against Akira Tozawa. Gentleman Jack Gallagher attempts to end his rivalry with The Brian Kendrick with an old-fashioned duel. Plus, the WWE Universe is introduced to the newest addition to the 205 Live roster.

episodes.name: August 29, 2017 (Little Rock, AR)
episodes.overview: In a No Disqualification Match, Gentleman Jack Gallagher faces The Brian Kendrick. Enzo Amore makes his 205 Live in-ring debut when he teams up with Gran Metalik & Cedric Alexander to take on Noam Dar, Drew Gulak & Tony Nese. Plus, Rich Swann battles Ariya Daivari as TJP provides ringside commentary.

episodes.name: September 5, 2017 (Sioux Falls, SD)
episodes.overview: See a Fatal 5-Way Match to determine who will face Neville for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship at No Mercy. TJP looks to shake off his recent injury when he goes one on one with Ariya Daivari. Plus, Drew Gulak has a very special presentation for a "Better 205 Live," but Akira Tozawa has other plans for the future of the Cruiserweight Division.

episodes.name: September 12, 2017 (Las Vegas, NV)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann and TJP bring their friendly rivalry to an end as they face off in their 3rd match. Cedric Alexander looks to build on his momentum from last week as he battles The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Drew Gulak picks up from where he left off on how to create a better 205 Live.

episodes.name: September 19, 2017 (Oakland, CA)
episodes.overview: Enzo Amore and the WWE Cruiserweight Champion Neville have their final face-to-face just five days before their championship match at No Mercy. Plus, Cedric Alexander looks for some revenge on The Brian Kendrick after his match against him was cut short last week, Drew Gulak keeps his PowerPoint Presentation going, and more!

episodes.name: September 26, 2017 (Glendale, AZ)
episodes.overview: Enzo Amore addresses the WWE Universe following his controversial WWE Cruiserweight Championship victory. Also, TJP is in singles action as he takes on the Golden Lynx of Lucha Libre, Lince Dorado. Plus, Akira Tozawa faces off with the Premier Athlete Tony Nese and more.

episodes.name: October 3, 2017 (Denver, CO)
episodes.overview: Kalisto makes his 205 Live debut when he takes on Ariya Daivari. Also, Drew Gulak continues his proposal for a better 205 Live, but an old foe in Mustafa Ali tries to show that 205 Live is just fine the way it is. Plus, Cedric Alexander looks for revenge on Gentleman Jack Gallagher and more.

episodes.name: October 10, 2017 (Grand Rapids, MI)
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Kalisto addresses the WWE Universe. Plus, Rich Swann and TJP finally look to bring their rivalry to an end when they face off in a 2 out of 3 Falls Match. Also, Drew Gulak looks to continue spreading his message for a better 205 Live when he faces a man that demonstrates everything wrong with 205 Live in Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: October 17, 2017 (Seattle, WA)
episodes.overview: Enzo Amore teams up with Ariya Daivari to take on Mustafa Ali and the WWE Cruiserweight Champion Kalisto. Gentleman Jack Gallagher takes on Rich Swann. Plus, Drew Gulak presents another Power Point slide on how to make a better 205 Live.

episodes.name: October 24, 2017 (Milwaukee, WI)
episodes.overview: Enzo Amore defends the Cruiserweight Championship against Kalisto. Rich Swann & Cedric Alexander team up again after to take on the team of Noam Dar & Tony Nese. Plus, Drew Gulak continues to spread his views on how to make a better 205 Live when he faces off with Gran Metalik.

episodes.name: October 31, 2017 (Norfolk, VA)
episodes.overview: This special Halloween edition of 205 Live features a Fright Night Fatal 4-Way match between Mustafa Ali, Tony Nese, Ariya Daivari, and Gran Metalik. Rich Swann isn't clowning around anymore when he takes on The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Drew Gulak delivers a different kind of PowerPoint presentation.

episodes.name: November 7, 2017 (Manchester, ENG)
episodes.overview: Emanating from the United Kingdom, this edition of 205 Live features the debut of the 'Zo Show, hosted by Cruiserweight Champion Enzo Amore. Gentleman Jack Gallagher takes on Kalisto. Plus, Cedric Alexander teams up with Mark Andrews to take on Joseph Conners & James Drake.

episodes.name: November 14, 2017 (Charlotte, NC)
episodes.overview: Kalisto celebrates his Birthday by facing off with Drew Gulak. Cedric Alexander teams up with Rich Swann to take on Gentleman Jack Gallagher & The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Mustafa Ali and Ariya Daivari go one-on-one in singles action.

episodes.name: November 21, 2017 (Houston, TX)
episodes.overview: It's a Thanksgiving Celebration as Drew Gulak faces off with Akira Tozawa in a Street Fight, Tony Nese goes one-on-one with Mustafa Ali, and Ariya Daivari teams up with Noam Dar to take on the team of Rich Swann & Cedric Alexander. Plus, we get a look at a new Superstar who will be coming to 205 Live soon.

episodes.name: November 28, 2017 (Lexington, KY)
episodes.overview: 'Zo Train members Tony Nese & Drew Gulak face off against the team of Cedric Alexander and Mustafa Ali. Rich Swann goes one-on-one with another 'Zo Train member in Noam Dar. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher faces off with Kalisto and more.

episodes.name: December 5, 2017 (San Diego, CA)
episodes.overview: Rich Swann faces off with 'Zo Train member Tony Nese. Noam Dar goes one on one with Cedric Alexander. Plus, The Brian Kendrick and Gentleman Jack Gallagher continue their dominance over 205 Live as Kendrick battles Gran Metalik.

episodes.name: December 12, 2017 (Cincinnati, OH)
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander faces off with 'Zo Train member Ariya Daivari. Kalisto looks to get payback on Gentleman Jack Gallagher after Gallagher and The Brian Kendrick attacked him a few weeks ago. Plus, Enzo Amore must take matters into his own hands so that he can get the 'Zo Train back on track.

episodes.name: December 19, 2017 (Newark, NJ)
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander looks to build some momentum when he takes on 'Zo Train member, Drew Gulak. Kalisto gets some backup as he and Gran Metalik team up to face off with The Brian Kendrick & Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, Hideo Itami makes his 205 Live debut when he goes one-on-one with Colin Delaney.

episodes.name: December 26, 2017 (Chicago, IL)
episodes.overview: In this special Christmas edition of 205 Live, Mustafa Ali & Cedric Alexander take on 'Zo Train member's Drew Gulak & Ariya Daivari. Also, Hideo Itami goes toe-to-toe with Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, Tony Nese tries to figure out what path is best as he faces off with Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: January 2, 2018
episodes.overview: Goldust makes his debut despite being a few pounds over the 205-pound weight limit to team up with Cedric Alexander to take on Drew Gulak & Ariya Daivari. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher calls out Hideo Itami. Also, we have the return of a man we haven’t seen in quite some time on 205 Live and much more action.

episodes.name: January 9, 2018
episodes.overview: TJP goes one-on-one with the Crown Jewel of Lucha Libre Gran Metalik. Also, Jack Gallagher has few words for Hideo Itami after Gallagher attacked him with a pipe last week. Plus, the 'Zo Train looks to chug on after their leader Enzo Amore suffered an ankle injury in a Championship defense against Cedric Alexander a night earlier on Raw.

episodes.name: January 16, 2018
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander gets a Golden Opportunity to learn from one of WWE's best veterans in Goldust. Also, the first-ever Cruiserweight Champion TJP looks to get some retribution when he faces off with Gran Metalik. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher has some words for the man he has set his sights on, Hideo Itami.

episodes.name: January 23, 2018
episodes.overview: The rivalry between Hideo Itami and Gentleman Jack Gallagher reaches a breaking point as these two go one-on-one. Two of the most dynamic Superstars in the entire Cruiserweight Division face off in an incredible match when Cedric Alexander battles Mustafa Ali. Plus, Kalisto, Gran Metalik & Lince Dorado battle TJP, Tony Nese & Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: January 30, 2018
episodes.overview: We find who will be the first-ever General Manager of 205 Live, and what he or she has in plan for the vacant WWE Cruiserweight Championship. Also, we will hear from some of the cruiserweights about what they think would be done for their brand and futures. Plus, we will have some incredible non-stop action as always.

episodes.name: February 6, 2018
episodes.overview: Round one of the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament continues with two more matches. The first matchup this week will feature two brothers of Lucha Libre when Kalisto takes on Lince Dorado. Also, Roderick Strong will make his 205 Live debut when he faces off with Hideo Itami in a first-round matchup.

episodes.name: February 13, 2018
episodes.overview: Round one of the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament continues with two more matches. The first matchup this week will feature a newcomer to 205 Live in Mark Andrews when he takes on former Cruiserweight Champion Akira Tozawa. Also, two good friends and often tag team partners Tony Nese and Drew Gulak face off in round one.

episodes.name: February 20, 2018
episodes.overview: Round one of the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament comes to the end with two more matches. The first matchup this week features Buddy Murphy taking on a veteran in Ariya Daivari Also, the high-flying Mustafa Ali will go toe-to-toe with Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, a preview of the quarterfinals.

episodes.name: February 27, 2018
episodes.overview: The quarterfinals kickoff with two huge matchups. First, early tournament favorite Cedric Alexander goes one-on-one with a man who knows a little something about tournaments in TJP. The second matchup will involve new comer Roderick Strong facing off with former Cruiserweight Champion Kalisto.

episodes.name: March 6, 2018
episodes.overview: The quarterfinals come to an end with two huge matchups. First, Drew Gulak goes one-on-one with Mark Andrews. The second matchup will involve Buddy Murphy facing off with one of the true favorites in this tournament in Mustafa Ali.

episodes.name: March 13, 2018
episodes.overview: The semifinals to crown a new WWE Cruiserweight Champion at WrestleMania kick-off when tournament favorite Cedric Alexander tries to end the Cinderella story that is Roderick Strong. Also, Hideo Itami & Akira Tozawa face-off with Gran Metalik & Lince Dorado. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher in action.

episodes.name: March 20, 2018
episodes.overview: The semifinals of the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament come to an end when Drew Gulak faces off against Mustafa Ali to see who will take on Cedric Alexander for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship at WrestleMania. Lince Dorado goes one-on-one with Hideo Itami. Plus, TJP is in action with something to prove to the entire WWE Universe.

episodes.name: March 27, 2018
episodes.overview: A Fatal 4-Way main event match between Akira Tozawa, Kalisto, TJP, and Buddy Murphy. Also, The Premier Athlete Tony Nese goes one-on-one with Mark Andrews. Plus, get a special preview of the Cruiserweight Championship Match at WrestleMania when Drake Maverick sits down with Cedric Alexander and Mustafa Ali.

episodes.name: April 3, 2018
episodes.overview: An in-depth preview at the Cruiserweight Championship Match at WrestleMania between Mustafa Ali and Cedric Alexander. Also, Buddy Murphy is back on 205 Live yet again when he faces off with former Cruiserweight Champion Kalisto. Plus, Lince Dorado and Gran Metalik team up to take on Hideo Itami and Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: April 10, 2018
episodes.overview: The Age of Alexander begins with a Cruiserweight celebration for the new champion, Cedric Alexander, who defeated Mustafa Ali at WrestleMania in the Finals of the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament. Also, Drew Gulak looks to silence the entire 205 Live locker room as he brings an end to the high flying and stage diving of Mark Andrews.

episodes.name: April 17, 2018
episodes.overview: A Tornado Tag Team main event has the Lucha House Party looking to get even with the team of Hideo Itami and Akira Tozawa, who have shown the luchadores little respect over the last few weeks. Mustafa Ali looks to build off his Cruiserweight Tournament success as he faces off with Ariya Daivari. Plus, The Brian Kendrick is back in action!

episodes.name: April 24, 2018
episodes.overview: This week on a very special edition of 205 Live we come to you from Louisville Kentucky and we will have a Five-Man Gauntlet Match to determine who will face the newly crowned Cedric Alexander for the Cruiserweight Championship at the Greatest Royal Rumble Live from the King Abdullah Sports City Stadium in the beautiful Jeddah, Saudi Arabia.

episodes.name: May 1, 2018
episodes.overview: The Brian Kendrick returns to in-ring action when he teams up with Jack Gallagher to take on Hideo Itami & Akira Tozawa. Buddy Murphy meets the required weight needed to compete on 205 Live. Plus, the aggressive and tactical Drew Gulak faces off with a former Cruiserweight Champion and member of the Lucha House Party, Kalisto.

episodes.name: May 8, 2018
episodes.overview: Buddy Murphy looks to erase the only blemish on his 205 Live record when he takes on Mustafa Ali in a rematch from the Cruiserweight Championship Tournament. Lucha House Party members Gran Metalik & Lince Dorado face-off versus Gentleman Jack Gallagher & The Brian Kendrick. Plus, an in-depth look at Hideo Itami and his recent actions.

episodes.name: May 15, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Superstars from the WWE's United Kingdom Division make their mark in 205 Live. TJP, Kalisto, Kenny Williams, and former United Kingdom Champion Tyler Bate battle in a Fatal 4-Way Match. Plus, Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander, Mustafa Ali, & Flash Morgan Webster take on James Drake, Joseph Connors, & Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: May 22, 2018
episodes.overview: An epic main event as former tag team partners Akira Tozawa and Hideo Itami look to settle their feud. Also, Drew Gulak faces off against Lucha House Party member Gran Metalik. Plus, WWE Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander sits down with Vic Joseph to discuss his thoughts on his upcoming Championship match against Buddy Murphy.

episodes.name: May 29, 2018
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander defends his Cruiserweight Championship against the unstoppable Buddy Murphy. Also, Lucha House Party looks to keep the celebration alive as they face off against the tactical duo of The Brian Kendrick & Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, a special announcement from General Manager Drake Maverick.

episodes.name: June 5, 2018
episodes.overview: Buddy Murphy takes on Mustafa Ali in the main event and gets back into the Cruiserweight Championship picture. Also, The Brian Kendrick looks to impress Drew Gulak when Kendrick goes one-on-one with Lince Dorado. Plus, TJP continues to prove to General Manager Drake Maverick that he still has what made him the first Cruiserweight Champion.

episodes.name: June 12, 2018
episodes.overview: Mustafa Ali looks to put himself back into Cruiserweight Championship contention when he takes on "The Premier Athlete" Tony Nese. Lucha House Party hopes to keep the celebrations going when they face off against Drew Gulak, Gentleman Jack Gallagher & The Brian Kendrick. Plus, Akira Tozawa looks to bounce back as a singles competitor.

episodes.name: June 19, 2018
episodes.overview: Mustafa Ali, Buddy Murphy, and Hideo Itami look to settle their differences in a Triple Threat Match. TJP continues to prove that he deserves better treatment and competition than what General Drake Maverick has given him over the last few weeks. Plus, Lucha House Party member Lince Dorado goes one-on-one with Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: June 26, 2018
episodes.overview: Six superstars look to claim team supremacy when Lucha House Party takes on the newly formed alliance of Drew Gulak, Gentleman Jack Gallagher & The Brian Kendrick. Cruiserweight Champion Akira Tozawa takes on "The Premier Athlete" Tony Nese. Plus, Lio Rush makes his highly anticipated 205 Live debut.

episodes.name: July 3, 2018
episodes.overview: Mustafa Ali faces off with the Buddy Murphy in a No Disqualification Match main event. Also, Noam Dar makes his return to 205 Live after being sidelined the past few months with an injury. Plus, Lio Rush takes a vested interest in one of our best competitors!

episodes.name: July 10, 2018
episodes.overview: The Soul of 205 Live Cedric Alexander defends his Cruiserweight Championship against the Japanese Legend, Hideo Itami. Plus, the Man of the Hour, Lio Rush is in action but gets a surprise visitor at ringside. Also, Lucha House Party member Kalisto faces off with the Premier Athlete, Tony Nese in a Singles Match.

episodes.name: July 17, 2018
episodes.overview: "The Man of the Hour" Lio Rush takes on former Cruiserweight Champion Akira Tozawa. Is he ready for prime time at the young age of 23, or will Tozawa put a stop to the rush? Also, TJP takes on the "Scottish Supernova" Noam Dar in a hotly anticipated rematch two weeks after Noam overwhelmed TJP in just 30 seconds.

episodes.name: July 24, 2018
episodes.overview: Former Cruiserweight Champion TJP, submission specialist Drew Gulak, Japanese legend Hideo Itami and "The Heart of 205" Mustafa Ali compete in a Fatal 4-Way Match for a future Cruiserweight Championship opportunity against Cedric Alexander. Also, Akira Tozawa faces Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, it’s a Lucha House Party on this 205 Live!

episodes.name: July 31, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander takes on "The Man with a Plan" The Brian Kendrick. The Premier Athlete looks to silence the Lucha House Party when he meets the high-flying Kalisto. Plus, Lio Rush is out to show Akira Tozawa that he is, in fact, The Man of the Hour.

episodes.name: August 7, 2018
episodes.overview: "The Heart of 205 Live" Mustafa Ali has his request for competition answered as he goes one-on-one with Hideo Itami. Also, Noam Dar looks to regain his momentum as he battles NXT challenger Sean Maluta. Plus, Lince Dorado and Kalisto take on the powerhouse duo of Buddy Murphy and Tony Nese.

episodes.name: August 14, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander takes on Gentleman Jack Gallagher in a Non-Title Match. Gallagher's associates Drew Gulak and The Brian Kendrick are banned from ringside. Plus, Akira Tozawa gets his much-anticipated rematch with The Man of the Hour Lio Rush. General Manager Drake Maverick makes a major announcement regarding Mustafa Ali.

episodes.name: August 21, 2018
episodes.overview: Lucha House Party sets out to prove that skill is more important than size when they take on Buddy Murphy & Tony Nese in a Tag Team Tornado Match main event. TJP and Noam Dar look to settle their rivalry once and for all. Drew Gulak demands a rematch against Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander. Akira Tozawa faces Colin Delaney.

episodes.name: August 28, 2018
episodes.overview: Buddy Murphy tangles with Lucha House Party member Kalisto in the main event. Akira Tozawa seeks revenge against The Brian Kendrick, with Gentleman Jack Gallagher in his corner, for attacking him during the previous edition of 205 Live. Hideo Itami faces newcomer Michael Blaise. Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander has a warning for Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: September 4, 2018
episodes.overview: Tony Nese takes on Lucha House Party member The King of the Ropes Gran Metalik. Noam Dar competes in singles action against Bryan Kelly. Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander calls out Drew Gulak and finds himself in the main event match against TJP. General Manager Drake Maverick admonishes Mustafa Ali for competing without medical clearance.

episodes.name: September 11, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander & Akira Tozawa take on Drew Gulak and Gentleman Jack Gallagher in the main event. After defeating Buddy Murphy's training partner Tony Nese last week, Lucha House Party's The King of the Ropes Gran Metalik faces Murphy for the first time. Mustafa Ali returns to in-ring action after weeks away due to injury.

episodes.name: September 19, 2018
episodes.overview: The Soul of 205 Live Cedric Alexander defends his Cruiserweight Championship against Drew Gulak in a huge main event match. TJP takes on Lucha House Party member Lince Dorado. General Manager Drake Maverick has some demands for The Man of the Hour Lio Rush and gives Mustafa Ali some eagerly anticipated news.

episodes.name: September 26, 2018
episodes.overview: Mustafa Ali looks to get retribution on Hideo Itami after being sidelined by the Japanese legend a few weeks prior. Lio Rush and Noam Dar settle their war of words in the ring. Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander and No. 1 contender Buddy Murphy have a face-to-face confrontation before their match at Super Show-Down.

episodes.name: October 3, 2018
episodes.overview: Two former Cruiserweight Champions face-off as TJP takes on the leader of the Lucha House Party, Kalisto. Akira Tozawa battles Gentleman Jack Gallagher, who will have The Brian Kendrick and Drew Gulak in his corner. Plus, Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander and No. 1 contender Buddy Murphy go in-depth on their upcoming match at Super Show-Down.

episodes.name: October 10, 2018
episodes.overview: Tony Nese accepts Cedric Alexander's demand for a match in the main event. The Man of the Hour Lio Rush looks to prove his exceptional talent by issuing an open challenge to the 205 Live Superstars. Mike and Maria Kanellis make an impactful statement. Drew Gulak and Gentleman Jack Gallagher explain their attack on former partner The Brian Kendrick.

episodes.name: October 17, 2018
episodes.overview: Cedric Alexander, Tony Nese, Gran Metalik, TJP, and Lio Rush compete in a Fatal 5-Way Match. Drew Gulak, with Gentleman Jack Gallagher in his corner, battles Akira Tozawa. New Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy makes his first appearance on 205 Live since winning the title. Mustafa Ali makes Hideo Itami a promise.

episodes.name: October 24, 2018
episodes.overview: 205 Live celebrates its 100th episode with a pair of main event-quality matches. Hideo Itami battles Mustafa Ali in a Falls Count Anywhere Match. Mike Kanellis faces Lince Dorado. The Brian Kendrick offers a warning to Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy has a message for General Manager Drake Maverick.

episodes.name: October 31, 2018
episodes.overview: A new No. 1 contender to the Cruiserweight Championship is determined as The Heart of 205 Live Mustafa Ali faces Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy's training partner The Premier Athlete Tony Nese. Former partners collide as The Brian Kendrick battles Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Gran Metalik takes on Tyson Dean.

episodes.name: November 7, 2018
episodes.overview: Buddy Murphy competes in his first match since winning the Cruiserweight Championship when he takes on the WWE's UK Division's Mark Andrews. General Manager Drake Maverick makes a major announcement for Survivor Series. TJP & Mike Kanellis face Lucha House Party's Kalisto & Lince Dorado. The Man of the Hour Lio Rush battles Josh Morrell.

episodes.name: November 14, 2018
episodes.overview: Former Cruiserweight Champion Cedric Alexander looks to get back on track when he faces Lio Rush. Former rivals The Brian Kendrick and Akira Tozawa team up for the first time to take on Drew Gulak & Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy and No. 1 contender Mustafa Ali have their Survivor Series weigh-in.

episodes.name: November 21, 2018
episodes.overview: TJP squares off against Lucha House Party's Gran Metalik. The Premier Athlete Tony Nese looks to climb the Cruiserweight ranks when he faces off with The Scottish Supernova Noam Dar. Mustafa Ali reacts to his loss at Survivor Series. The Brian Kendrick & Akira Tozawa compete in tag team action.

episodes.name: November 28, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy teams with his training partner and best friend The Premier Athlete Tony Nese to take on Cedric Alexander & Mustafa Ali. Hideo Itami returns to action in a one-on-one match against newcomer Levy Cruise. Mike Kanellis faces The Scottish Supernova Noam Dar. TJP demands a Cruiserweight Championship match.

episodes.name: December 5, 2018
episodes.overview: The Lucha House Party looks to settle their score with TJP & Mike Kanellis in a Tornado Tag Team Match. Also, The Brian Kendrick looks to get retribution on his former comrade Drew Gulak when they compete one-on-one in singles action. Plus, Ariya Daivari makes his in-ring return after being out of action for months with an injury.

episodes.name: December 12, 2018
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy takes on Gran Metalik in singles action, while his opponent at WWE TLC, Cedric Alexander, faces Murphy's training buddy the Premier Athlete Tony Nese. Plus, hear from not only Drew Gulak & Gentleman Jack Gallagher but also The Brian Kendrick & Akira Tozawa looking ahead to their upcoming tag team Street Fight.

episodes.name: December 19, 2018
episodes.overview: The Brian Kendrick teams up with Akira Tozawa to take on his former allies Drew Gulak and Jack Gallagher in a Street Fight where anything goes. The Man of the Hour Lio Rush returns to the ring. Also, hear from Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy and Cedric Alexander following their match at WWE TLC. Plus, Hideo Itami in action.

episodes.name: December 26, 2018
episodes.overview: Vic Joseph, Nigel McGuinness, and Percy Watson take a look back at the most memorable matches and top 10 moments from 2018 in the WWE Cruiserweight Division. Plus, go in-depth on what 2019 holds for WWE Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy.

episodes.name: January 2, 2019 (Pittsburgh, PA)
episodes.overview: 205 Live kicks off 2019 with a pair of qualification matches for the Fatal 4-Way Match for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship at the Royal Rumble pay-per-view. In the first qualification match, Kalisto takes on the Man of the Hour Lio Rush. The second match sees Drew Gulak face Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: January 9, 2019 (Jacksonville, FL)
episodes.overview: The final qualification match for the Cruiserweight Championship Fatal 4-Way at the Royal Rumble sees Cedric Alexander take on Hideo Itami. Plus, The Scottish Super Nova Noam Dar faces Tony Nese in a rematch from last month when Buddy Murphy helped Nese get the win.

episodes.name: January 15, 2019 (Birmingham, AL)
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy's open challenge is answered by a debuting Cruiserweight. The Man of the Hour Lio Rush battles Lucha House Party's Lince Dorado. Tony Nese confronts Noam Dar. TJP wants a new opportunity.

episodes.name: January 22, 2019 (Wichita, KS)
episodes.overview: The three contenders to the WWE Cruiserweight Championship on the Royal Rumble kickoff show, Kalisto, Hideo Itami, and Akira Tozawa, compete in a Triple Threat Match. In his first official match as a member of the 205 Live roster, Humberto Carrillo takes on Gran Metalik.

episodes.name: January 29, 2019 (Phoenix, AZ)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have a huge main event match up when former tag team partners face off when Akira Tozawa takes on Hideo Itami. Plus, Mike Kanellis looks to build some momentum and show Drake Maverick he has what it takes to be Cruiserweight Champion when he goes one on one with a former Cruiserweight Champion in Kalisto.

episodes.name: February 5, 2019 (Everett, WA)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have a huge main event when Cedric Alexander, Akira Tozawa, Lio Rush, and Humberto Carrillo face off in a Fatal 4-Way to determine who will become the number one contender and face Buddy Murphy for the Cruiserweight Championship at Elimination Chamber.

episodes.name: February 12, 2019 (Toledo, OH)
episodes.overview: On this edition of 205 Live, a huge main event sees 'The Scottish Supernova' Noam Dar and 'The Premier Athlete' Tony Nese try to settle their differences in a No Disqualification Match. Plus, Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy and Akira Tozawa meet to sign the contract for their match at Elimination Chamber!

episodes.name: February 19, 2019 (New Orleans, LA)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, Mike Kanellis looks to finally have all his hard work pay off when he faces off with a former Cruiserweight Champion in Cedric Alexander who is looking to get his 2019 on track as well. Also, Ariya Daivari is in action and is no longer holding back how he feels about 205 Live and the WWE Universe.

episodes.name: February 26, 2019 (Charlotte, NC)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we kick off the No. 1 Contender's Tournament for the Cruiserweight Championship at WrestleMania with two huge matchups. The Premier Athlete, Tony Nese, faces off with a former Cruiserweight Champion, Kalisto. Also, The Brian Kendrick goes toe-to-toe with one of his former allies, the Punishing Drew Gulak.

episodes.name: March 5, 2019 (Wilkes-Barre, PA)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have the final two first-round matchups in the No. 1 Contender's Tournament for the Cruiserweight Championship. In the first matchup, Humberto Carrillo goes one-on-one with special guest Oney Lorcan. The second matchup gives us a face-off with two former Cruiserweight Champions in Akira Tozawa and Cedric Alexander.

episodes.name: March 12, 2019 (Dayton, OH)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have the two Semifinal matchups in the No. 1 Contender's Tournament for the Cruiserweight Championship. The first match features former Champion Cedric Alexander facing off with the NXT invite Oney Lorcan. In the second Semifinal matchup, Drew Gulak looks to top Tony Nese once again.

episodes.name: March 19, 2019 (Indianapolis, IN)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have the final matchup in the No. 1 Contender's Tournament for the Cruiserweight Championship when The Premier Athlete Tony Nese faces off with last year's Tournament winner Cedric Alexander. The winner will have the incredible task of trying to defeat Buddy Murphy at WrestleMania to capture the Cruiserweight Title.

episodes.name: March 26, 2019 (Uncasville, CT)
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we have a huge main event matchup when Cedric Alexander looks to rebound from his loss last week to Tony Nese when he takes on Ariya Daivari. Plus, we will hear from our Cruiserweight Champion Buddy Murphy and how he feels about facing his former ally in Tony Nese at WrestleMania.

episodes.name: April 2, 2019
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we take a very special look into the Cruiserweight Championship Match at WrestleMania between the champion Buddy Murphy and the challenger Tony Nese. Plus, Kalisto takes on the newest addition to the 205 Live roster, Oney Lorcan, and Mike Kanellis looks to keep his hot streak going when he goes one on one with Akira Tozawa.

episodes.name: April 9, 2019
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, Tony Nese defends his newly acquired WWE Cruiserweight Championship against the former champion Buddy Murphy, just days after their epic battle at WrestleMania. Humberto Carrillo gets the opportunity to learn how to properly handle yourself in a 205 Live ring from Gentleman Jack Gallagher.

episodes.name: April 16, 2019
episodes.overview: After being shifted to Raw in the Superstar Shake-up, 'The Soul of 205 Live' Cedric Alexander has his farewell match against Oney Lorcan. Also, now that he has moved on from Buddy Murphy, Tony Nese seeks a new challenger in the winner of a huge Fatal 4-Way Match between Akira Tozawa, Mike Kanellis, Gran Metalik and Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: April 23, 2019
episodes.overview: Ariya Daivari and Oney Lorcan battle for a future WWE Cruiserweight Championship opportunity against titleholder Tony Nese. Also, Drew Gulak looks to teach a former apprentice a lesson when he takes on Humberto Carrillo, who has a few tricks up his sleeve as he sets out to prove that flight might just be right.

episodes.name: April 30, 2019
episodes.overview: The Singh Brothers make their return to 205 Live when they face off against the strong and confident Lucha House Party in tag-team action. Also, Tony Nese looks to end his rivalry with Drew Gulak, as the Cruiserweight Champion goes one-on-one with the Voice and Reason of 205 Live. Plus, The Brian Kendrick is in action.

episodes.name: May 7, 2019
episodes.overview: In a main event that has been weeks in the making, Akira Tozawa and Mike Kanellis look to end their rivalry in a No Disqualification Match. Ariya Daivari goes head-to-head with Noam Dar, just weeks before his Cruiserweight Championship match against Tony Nese at Money in the Bank. Plus, the Singh Brothers are in Tag-Team action.

episodes.name: May 14, 2019
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, we come to you from across the pond in London as the Superstars of 205 Live mix it up with the Superstars of NXT UK. 205 Live's Gentleman Jack Gallagher and Humberto Carillo meet NXT UK's James Drake and Mark Andrews in a Fatal 4-Way. Cruiserweight Champion Tony Nese faces off with the International Icon, Ligero.

episodes.name: May 21, 2019
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, The Brian Kendrick, Akira Tozawa, Mike Kanellis, Oney Lorcan and Ariya Daivari compete in a Fatal 5-Way Match. Also, we will take a look back to the epic Cruiserweight Championship match at Money in the Bank where Tony Nese successfully defended his title against Ariya Daivari. Plus, the Singh Brothers are in tag team action.

episodes.name: May 28, 2019
episodes.overview: This week on 205 Live, Gentleman Jack Gallagher and Humberto Carrillo face off in the Main Event to settle their score over the last few weeks. Also, The Brian Kendrick goes one on one with Mike Kanellis and the Scottish Super Nova, Noam Dar, is in action.

episodes.name: June 4, 2019
episodes.overview: Ariya Daivari looks to get revenge on Oney Lorcan. The Scottish Super Nova, Noam Dar, looks to cement himself in the Cruiserweight Championship picture as he takes on one of the top dogs in the division, Akira Tozawa. Plus, we will hear from the Lucha House Party just days before their handicap match against Lars Sullivan at Super ShowDown.

episodes.name: June 11, 2019
episodes.overview: Ariya Daivari looks to get revenge on Oney Lorcan. The Scottish Super Nova, Noam Dar, looks to cement himself in the Cruiserweight Championship picture as he takes on one of the top dogs in the division, Akira Tozawa. Plus, we will hear from the Lucha House Party just days before their handicap match against Lars Sullivan at Super ShowDown.

episodes.name: June 18, 2019
episodes.overview: After a controversial ending to the Fatal 4-Way match for the No.1 contender's spot at Stomping Grounds for the Cruiserweight Championship, Drake Maverick must determine who will face Tony Nese. The Lucha House Party looks to put their rivalry to bed when they face the Singh Brothers in Tag-Team action. Plus, The Brian Kendrick is in action.

episodes.name: June 25, 2019
episodes.overview: Akira Tozawa and Tony Nese face off in a No. 1 Contenders Match to determine who will face Drew Gulak at Extreme Rules. Mike Kanellis looks to prove once again that he is the best Superstar in the division when he takes on Gentleman Jack Gallagher.

episodes.name: July 2, 2019
episodes.overview: Tony Nese, Oney Lorcan and Jack Gallagher take on Drew Gulak, Ariya Daivari and Mike Kanellis in a Six-Man Tag Team match. The Singh Brothers look to put their rivalry to an end with the Lucha House Party as they face off in a Tornado Tag match. Plus, take an in depth look at one of newer members of the 205 Live roster, Humberto Carrillo.

episodes.name: July 9, 2019
episodes.overview: Oney Lorcan and Ariya Daivari look to settle their score when they face off in an Anything Goes match in the main event. The Brian Kendrick looks to silence the Bollywood Duo known as the Singh Brothers. Plus, Gentleman Jack Gallagher is in action.

episodes.name: July 16, 2019
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Drew Gulak reacts to his victory at Extreme Rules. Samir Singh faces Tozawa. Mike Kanellis tries to prove his greatness to Drake Maverik. Gentleman Jack Gallagher faces Chad Gable.

episodes.name: July 23, 2019
episodes.overview: WWE Cruiserweight Champion Drew Gulak faces NXT Superstar Isaiah "Swerve" Scott in the main event. Oney Lorcan, Humberto Carrillo, Lucha House Party and more are in action. Plus, 205 Live General Manager Drake Maverick and Mike Kanellis sign the contract for their impending Unsanctioned Match.

episodes.name: July 30, 2019
episodes.overview: Mike Kanellis battles Drake Maverick in an Unsanctioned Match. If Kanellis wins, he gets an opportunity to challenge for the WWE Cruiserweight Championship. The Brian Kendrick & Akira Tozawa take on Singh Brothers. Lince Dorado takes on Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: August 6, 2019
episodes.overview: Oney Lorcan, Tony Nese, Kalisto, Gentleman Jack Gallagher, Akira Tozawa, and Ariya Daivari compete in a Six-Pack Challenge Match to determine the No. 1 Contender for the Cruiserweight Championship at SummerSlam. Plus, Humberto Carrillo battles Lince Dorado.

episodes.name: August 13, 2019
episodes.overview: In a SummerSlam rematch, Cruiserweight Champion Drew Gulak defends the title against Oney Lorcan. Lucha House Party members Kalisto and Lince Dorado team with Humberto Carrillo to face Ariya Daivari & The Singh Brothers, and much more.

episodes.name: August 20, 2019
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Drew Gulak and Oney Lorcan each lead a team in a Captain's Challenge 10-Man Tag Team Elimination Match. Featuring Angel Garza, Ariya Daivari, Mike Kanellis and Tony Nese on Gulak's team and Gentleman Jack Gallagher, Humberto Carrillo, Akira Tozawa and Isaiah "Swerve" Scott on Lorcan's team.

episodes.name: August 27, 2019
episodes.overview: Humberto Carrillo and Oney Lorcan battle to determine the No. 1 Contender for Drew Gulak's Cruiserweight Championship at Clash of Champions. Plus, Lucha House Party's Kalisto takes on Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: September 3, 2019
episodes.overview: Lince Dorado faces Humberto Carrillo for the chance to be added to the Cruiserweight Championship match at Clash of Champions. Mike Kanellis battles Tony Nese while The Brian Kendrick & Akira Tozawa take on Brandon Scott & Tyler Hastings.

episodes.name: September 10, 2019
episodes.overview: Lince Dorado, Gran Metalik & Humberto Carrillo take on Drew Gulak, Tony Nese & Ariya Daivari. Plus, Kushida makes his 205 Live debut teaming with Gentleman Jack Gallagher to face The Brian Kendrick & Akira Tozawa and more.

episodes.name: September 17, 2019
episodes.overview: Oney Lorcan takes on Tony Nese, The Brian Kendrick battles Gentleman Jack Gallagher, and Lince Dorado faces Ariya Daivari.

episodes.name: September 24, 2019
episodes.overview: Cruiserweight Champion Drew Gulak & Tony Nese take on Oney Lorcan & Danny Burch. Cousins collide as Humberto Carrillo faces Angel Garza.

episodes.name: October 11, 2019
episodes.overview: The Brian Kendrick battles Akira Tozawa in a No Disqualification Match. Plus, Oney Lorcan & Danny Burch take on Drew Gulak & Tony Nese and Ariya Daivari faces Chris Bey.

episodes.name: October 18, 2019
episodes.overview: The Brian Kendrick takes on Gentleman Jack Gallagher. Plus, Tony Nese faces Oney Lorcan & Ariya Daivari and The Singh Brothers battle Justin Alexander & Justin Morris.

episodes.overview: NXT Cruiserweight Champion Lio Rush faces Oney Lorcan, Tony Nese takes on Raul Mendoza and Isaiah "Swerve" Scott battles Ariya Daivari.
